1. Open the website that has the `mat-input-4` and `mat-input-5` inputs.
2. Open the Developer Tools in your browser (you can usually access them by right-clicking the page and selecting "Inspect" or by pressing F12 or Cmd+Option+I on Mac).
3. Click on the "Console" tab inside the Developer Tools.
4. Copy and paste the script provided above into the console.
5. Press Enter to run the script.

